  seerName: The Rotted Seer
  vigor: 7
  clarity: 5
  spirit: 11
  guard: 2
  traits:
  - 'Their withered touch is only contagious if

    they will it.'
  - 'Sees the way to live on through any

    amount of physical decay.'
  - 'Wants to become even more rotten, filthy,

    and diseased.

    A pact to
    uphold truth and fact

    On lies the false lay brake and cracked

    True
    Knight

    SYMBOL OF THE TRUTH

    Trigger Effect

    1 Lying to you about

    their
    identity Golden glow

    2 Giving false witness

    to you Turns cold

    3
    Giving you malicious

    advice Gentle hum

    4 Lying while bearing

    the
    shield Fragrant aroma

    5 Omitting key

    information to you Distant birdcall

    6
    Lying to you about

    their intent Loud clang'
